{"tid":838035,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【#Cult片】今個post唔直接介紹cult片，想簡單介紹吓《Troma》哩個電發行作公司。","createTime":"2018-09-26T22:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T05:33:15.000Z","uid":212112,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"01bdb9683ee620fa4f2ec2d83d6e689ac0a7b282","tid":838035,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T22:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/061837_d7dad8480ee8bd0e0c57a1d0cfb013b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F061837_d7dad8480ee8bd0e0c57a1d0cfb013b2.png&h=4db8e238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正所謂Troma出品必屬cult品，幾次觀看Troma公司出品電影後的直接感想，就是好奇如此低俗粗劣劇情和視覺特效，點解可以在電影界如此屹立不搖，而且每齣作品更是瘋癲得令人睇到眼都突，人體排泄物屎尿天上飛的奇觀令人著迷，爆頭腸流更是家常便飯，低俗品味真是無人能比。放眼看現今所有電影團體，真係好難找到一個和Troma一般品味惡劣的公司，這種瘋狂卻是Troma的賣點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/061838_846ae9acf3c86387d601b22b7672ca5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F061838_846ae9acf3c86387d601b22b7672ca5b.png&h=81ee0d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTroma影業公司已成立三十餘年，領導人是Lloyd Kaufman集製片、編劇、導演、演員於一身的全才。Troma的傳奇實際上也可以看作是Lloyd Kaufman的個人傳奇，是他主導了Troma的低俗口味並堅持不懈地將公司發展壯大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/061843_9b29c8b301aecf63e62a3f6dc2d2be46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F061843_9b29c8b301aecf63e62a3f6dc2d2be46.png&h=1294dc74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLloyd Kaufman說：Troma就是一個品牌。其背後的意義是，假若觀眾跑進戲院看我們的電影，就如經歷一次前所未有，而且永志難忘的冒險之旅。看後，可能你會厭惡我們至極，要不你因此愛死我們，甚至會認為Troma的電影是偉大的。Troma與眾不同處，便是他們的影片容易挑起了觀眾的情緒，Troma的電影內含著巨大的熱情，這正正是現今好萊塢電影所沒有的。Troma電影的拍攝目的是娛樂大眾，而觀眾亦真心真意喜歡這些電影。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/061839_68d2a33a6888570b3a26b0c5c5dd8297.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F061839_68d2a33a6888570b3a26b0c5c5dd8297.png&h=dd6c0a55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/061840_af883bf86caf2df2a9ea7cb720473ec6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F061840_af883bf86caf2df2a9ea7cb720473ec6.png&h=64453335&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/061841_fbc67c0a314d4e155401e0278ef35756.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F061841_fbc67c0a314d4e155401e0278ef35756.png&h=d3320f36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/061842_1c474966908f261f9fdc472285d8a935.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F061842_1c474966908f261f9fdc472285d8a935.png&h=77b46994&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/061844_5d96d96ef6ee8d6231e16a1a61536d6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F061844_5d96d96ef6ee8d6231e16a1a61536d6e.png&h=916fdc0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/Bm7x1bflQOJ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBm7x1bflQOJ%2F&d=fiJCY29iX%2FgwfSP31nRYpbZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=4a1a48c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBm7x1bflQOJ%2F&h=b65086e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/p/Bm7x1bflQOJ/</a>"},{"pid":"ea9f9b5a3eeea63e1807a9c3bdeef0ca6001e79e","tid":838035,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T22:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a177bc31a49544df44f8bda08627e8e61743b3","tid":838035,"uid":212112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2